# Personal / lifestyle apps — template for a private, machine-local Brewfile.
#
# `setup` copies this to `Brewfile.personal` (gitignored) on first run.
# Edit that copy with your own apps; entries below are commented-out examples,
# so a freshly seeded file installs nothing until you uncomment or add to it.

# Casks
# cask "google-chrome"  # Web browser
# cask "spotify"        # Music streaming
# cask "whatsapp"       # Messaging

# Formulae
# brew "ffmpeg"         # Audio/video processing
